Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Never Land (永无之乡)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狮牙」 你也还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.10,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 狮牙 (Dandelion) - AX派遣执行官里昂的代号 他被判处千年徒刑\N以任务来缩短其刑期的方式而替AX工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次能减多少年的刑期？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七千三百天 二十年左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是什么事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上个月开始 在艾伯塔恩的近海区域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,频繁发生吸血鬼袭击船舶的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从现场回收了某个人的遗骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.20,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 妖精 - 吸血鬼的一种\N藉由展开在背部的副肺排出空气 进行高速飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在吸血鬼当中 这也是稀有的品种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查结果证明 他并非是先天性的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是遭到后天「转向」的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.50,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 转向 - 被吸血的受害者 有机会成为另一个吸血鬼 这种人称之为「转向者」\N但发生的机率不到0.1% 是种极为罕见的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 是被制造的吸血鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原本是个孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像曾被这个人收养过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆士．巴雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦迪尼姆大学医学部前部长 艾伯塔恩的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经引退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在领地的小岛上 经营着小规模的孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是提不起干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种跟小孩子有关的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到小岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 冒烟了 烟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为租金很便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 在警告灯没亮之前都不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩之前要先帮田地浇水施肥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿做不也一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一起玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连卡莉也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 那些家伙要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 我来打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负温迪的家伙 由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉 其它人拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得坚强一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能着陆的更稳当点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小命还在就该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去的时候怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正无线电也坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 我们遇难了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 如果要我承受这样的考验的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如干脆死了算…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人快滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这个岛上的人吗 你父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授果然如传闻般地喜欢小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样照顾着从各地收养来的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也是被领养的孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要砂糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加十三份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三份？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但被你们所救 还请我喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是茶叶好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 果然还是泡茶的功夫好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里只有你们几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做菜和洗衣服的话 单靠我们也就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是想问神父一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…埃布尔•奈特罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇厅…国务圣省
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务分室…AX
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 神父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AX的人来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼、袭击船舶、处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自白剂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来杀我们的吗 此外还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授在什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有意识嘛 剂量太少了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊 神父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法见到巴雷教授了 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经得到了 绝不让大人妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是属于小孩们的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输给大叔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 小孩子怎么能赢过大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会变强给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得比大叔更强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强了后 准备干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护温迪 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不该笑你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强或弱不能拿来当借口 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己现在全部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保护心爱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够做到这点的话 你就是一个男子汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你的素质也不差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力个四、五年的话 肯定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我也能变得像大叔那么强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 能变得仅次于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉在你这么兴奋的时候打断你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我把埃布尔叫来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个看起来笨笨的眼镜神父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是「失败作」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以认为自己不能像成功品那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会努力的 努力成为大人 然后变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手真是意外的敏捷啊 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了我找你们的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢这么做 可恶的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高周波吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 我来救你了 跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个留在这里会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里吧 带我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样 不能成功「转向」而死掉的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「转向」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用人工方式制造吸血鬼 是巴雷教授的实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被输血 在肚子和背上植入奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授对大家做尽残酷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是温迪 每天都被欺负到哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要变成大人 我要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强后 就可以保护温迪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是「失败作」的我 温迪也总是温柔地对待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 你要到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直当个乖小孩的话 本来是可以好好相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你不同 他并没有逃避自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是了不起的男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不允许你污辱他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小仙子系统」 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.80,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 小仙子系统 - 在兵器"沉默之声"后被延伸开发出来的战术统御系统\N由"主人"与"下属"两种系统架构所组成.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的合作 是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众人即我 我即是众人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家以我的意志来行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 喜欢说场面话的神父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微铃系统被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人与下属式的战术统御系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是透过那个钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的思考传递给其它妖精 并进行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏掉钟 系统就瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是逮捕巴雷教授
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及消灭所有袭击船舶的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用杀掉他们啊 逮捕起来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做反而更加残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是「人为转向」成功的珍贵例子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.10,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 人为转向 - 使用违反自然法则的方式\N强制"转向"这个现象 并制造出"妖精"的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后几百年里 将会被当作人体实验的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得残酷的话 就祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们AX也是允许祈祷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不允许怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 不要杀温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪其实是很善良的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事 都只是照医生的命令做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在「永无之乡」的时间已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:50.10,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: Never Land (永无之乡) - 典故出自著名童话"Peter Pan"里\N主角彼得潘所居住的岛名 又称为"梦幻岛"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你不是很强吗 救救温迪 救救大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 拜托你 不要再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 就我一个当坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来怎么办 埃布尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经有办法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在永无之乡岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突袭了巴雷教授进行非法实验的藏身处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没能确认教授的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全灭了吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 公费清单中有一张奇怪的收据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说租了一艘货船什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物的目的地则是艾伯塔恩的伦迪尼姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金额也很庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:21:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是什么来着的 埃布尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是什么来着的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么这就不能判定是公费开销了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为你们的个人开支
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收款单将会转交给你们 请做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的金额 我实在是、实在是拿不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是吃牢饭的 哪有钱啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋 怎么不先想好借口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂你才是 一副信心十足的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我放心地以为你已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不考虑正是我的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我怎么会觉得你有考虑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 眼镜男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你刚才叫我笨蛋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是孩子气啊 两个人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 第八话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Noise (沉默之声)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别给我错过了
